channel.title: Should I release?
channel.description:
I'm having a lot of troubles at home, and a lot of personal shit; due this I don't feel like coding anymore, So I'm thinking about releasing my server (see signature) But not the version I'm at now but an older version of fantasy world.
I still want to keep the newest version (where is still worked on, by rodrigo I barely do anything anymore.) So If I manage to get some money here, might going to host it. Else it's for rodrigo
So what ya think should I release it so people can make it better instead of me doing nothing?
